Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.70,0:18:18.55,English,,0,0,0,,a relic of the distant past,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.70,0:18:18.55,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.55,0:18:22.29,English,,0,0,0,,but analog may now be making a comeback.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.55,0:18:22.29,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.29,0:18:26.43,English,,0,0,0,,There are startups actively working on analog computers.
